            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Tu viator qui tr</ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>ansis <expan><abbr>rest</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tit</abbr><ex>ulum</ex></expan> o<lb break="no" n="2"/>biter <expan><abbr>le</abbr><ex>ge</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>rep</abbr><ex>ete</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>uis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>erra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>evis</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Tzita qui et Vi<lb break="no" n="4"/>talis <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> et Florenti<lb break="no" n="5"/>us filius <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> et Vitalis <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> Tzita pater <lb n="7"/>posuit Laurentzio <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">f</supplied>ilio suo carissim<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Dreiecksgiebel mit Rosette; Z. 1 befindet sich innerhalb des Giebels. Z. 4 (Anfang): Buchstabe L unsicher, vielleicht LP-Ligatur. (B): CIL III; Beševliev: Leseabweichung.</p>
            </div>
